      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-accepting-c" mid="83" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="72"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>I have sent an army, but it was useless. There has already been a great loss due to the fight against the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon</FONT>, so the army is not strong enough to face <FONT color=#a82424>Serpentra</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
