      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-accepting-f" mid="87" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="76"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio${action:Talk}<BR>Who else would I be talking about besides <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint</FONT>?<BR>A dragon is certainly the strongest creature in this world. No matter how strong that Serpentra is, there is no way that it could beat a dragon.</html>]]></talk_question>
